---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Container from '../components/ui/Container.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | ChinaWebFoundry"
  description="ChinaWebFoundry privacy policy. How we collect, use, and protect your personal data."
>
  <section class="section-spacing">
    <Container>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="prose max-w-3xl text-[var(--color-text-body)]">
        <p>Last updated: 31 March 2026</p>

        <h2>1. Information we collect</h2>
        <p>We collect information you provide directly to us, such as when you fill out a contact form or subscribe to our newsletter. This may include your name, email address, company name, and any message you send us.</p>

        <h2>2. How we use your information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to respond to your enquiries, provide our services, send you updates you have opted into, and improve our website.</p>

        <h2>3. Data sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell your personal data. We may share your information with service providers who assist us in operating our website and delivering our services, subject to confidentiality obligations.</p>

        <h2>4. Data retention</h2>
        <p>We retain your personal data only for as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes for which it was collected, or as required by law.</p>

        <h2>5. Your rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. Contact us at the details below to exercise these rights.</p>

        <h2>6. Contact</h2>
        <p>For privacy-related enquiries, please contact us via our <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
